Hedging Strategies
Project: Hedging with Binomial Trees
Goal: Create a system to implement and visualize hedging strategies for European and exotic options.
Features:
Build a binomial tree model.
Simulate the hedging process using delta hedging.
Compare the portfolio value with and without hedging.
Advanced Add-On: Include stochastic volatility models to study how volatility impacts hedging.
Tools: Python, pandas, Plotly.
